AB  - The proceedings contain 163 papers. The special focus in this conference is on Materials Science and Engineering. The topics include: Research on mechanism in the SNCR DeNox process; investigation of low temperature sintering of low voltage varistor based on TiO2; direct immobilization of glucose oxidase on the hydrophilic copolymer support containing oxirane; ablation properties of ZrO2-MgO and Mo nozzle produced by plasma spray forming; identification of unknown sediment in water-reducer; zinc oxide production technology of distillation twice based on scrap miscellaneous zinc materials; effect of aluminium powder additives upon CO2 reactivity of electrolytic aluminium carbon anode with calcined anthracite; the effect of coating agent and preparation on the thermostability of coated potassium chlorate; dynamic recrystallization behavior of pure titanium; reaction heat of high alkali aluminosilicate glass batches in melting process; nano-rheology and its application in controlled-release fragrance nanocapsules suspensions; review of advanced technology of flue gas desulphurization; preparation and stability studies of a desulfurizer loaded on porous silica gel; preparation and properties of copper antibacterial silica; preparation and microstructure of exfoliated graphite with large expanding volume by two-step intercalation; wasted low grade iron ore with high phosphorus reuse for phosphate removal from aqueous solution by using a factorial design; university server room creep corrosion prevention; preparation and properties of porous poly(vinyl alcohol)/powdered activated carbon composite; dissolution of tungsten carbide in remanufacturing coating by plasma spray welding; research on the engineering properties of fly ash as backfill; the impact on the polypropylene matrix composites by the cutting size of the automotive interior decoration scrap; effect of pre-wetting super-light aggregate reinforced aerated concrete; effect of niobium on the morphology of nodular graphite in ductile iron; the residual stress after high frequency induction welding with complex shapes WC-Co alloy and steel; characterization of recycled cemented carbide and the raw materials; interface microstructure and properties of 304 austenite stainless steel/low carbon steel clad plate by casting and hot rolling process; thermodynamic optimization design of casting Mg-Zn-Cu alloy; first-principles study of the mechanical properties of ScAl microalloyed by 4d-transition metals; investigation into the post-treatment process for titanium alloy space-curve meshing-wheel; influence of the electric current pulse with different pulse width on the eutectoid microstructure of hypoeutectic Fe-C alloys; microstructural and mechanical properties of Al 7003 alloy processed by dual equal channel lateral extrusion; tribological properties of FeNiCr coatings with the addition of La2O3 on 1045 carbon steel; halide activators suitable for low temperature pack aluminisation of electroplated nickel on creep resistant ferritic steels; research and application on parameter optimizing of oxygen lance nozzle on converter for semi-steel making; a method for welding deviation acquisition based on magnetic-control arc sensing for multi-pass welding; characterization of calcium phosphate with an anodic TiO2 nanotube layer on titanium screw for biomedical application; preparation of environment-friendly epoxidized corn oil as a plasticizer; determination of diflubenzuron residues in vegetables by UPLC-MS/MS; determination of chlorbenzuron residues in tea by UPLC-MS/MS; determination of imidacloprid residues in Chinese cabbage by UPLC-MS/MS; preparation and electrical properties of multilayer zinc oxide varistor by gelcasting; ultraviolet photodetectors based on MgZnO thin films; high precision fiber DFB laser micro-accelerometer; the research on conductive fibers configuration of antistatic fabric; effect of electron beam irradiation crosslinking on PVA films; study on microstructure and tribological properties of graphite-like carbon films; high-performance indium oxide thin film transistor with ITO source/drain electrodes fabricated by reactive sputtering; soundscape of public space and design method; research and application of information operation and maintenance fault diagnosis model for power grid enterprise; software design methods research on configuration technology; a kind of traffic light controller simulation design; the design of speed acquisition and prompt system based on STC89C52; music spectrum display system based on MCU; adaptive USB fast charger design based on quick charge 2.0 protocol; study on micro-deformation monitoring technology of contacts for electric connectors; research on optical feature recognition technology of multiple micro-holes; design and simulation of the hydraulic loading control system of the rolling bearing fatigue life testing machine; a robust adaptive sliding mode control method for attitude control of the quad-rotor; study on unbalance compensation control of STATCOM based on MMC; variable frequency and multi-pressure water supply control system based on STM32 processor; fuzzy control of Z-source PV grid-connected using constant frequency hysteresis comparison; thermal stress compensation of MgO concrete in construction of high arch dams in cold areas; the study on the compensation for displacement of multi-way valve main spool; test research of vertical machine center's geometrical accuracy stabilization; mechanical properties of sandstone under loading and unloading conditions; finite element analysis for the welding column of CNC boring machine; comparison of the bearing capacity of dry and wet cutting surfaces; prediction of cutting force in trochoidal milling based on radial depth of cut; dynamic analysis of bionic vibration isolation platform based on viscoelastic materials; the factors sensitivity analysis of drift ice impact force on the pier; work hardening of the isotactic polypropylene during rolling; experimental study on impact damper with activated carbon fine particles; experimental research on the preparation of heat-resistant concrete using normal Portland cement; the effect of air pressure on the evolution of fiber path in melt-blowing process; a numerical study on hollow droplets impact onto a solid substrate; quantum discord of coupling qubits in decoherence-free subspace and squeezed vacuum reservoir; the motion attitude analysis of high-speed tracked vehicle climbing over vertical wall; finite element simulation and experimental research in insulation spacer blanking; research of sled motorcycle model design; the numerical control turning processing fixture design u-shaped thin-wall parts; vibration analysis and research on air bearing block of CMM; electric film based on the design of the new electrothermal furnace; innovative of the clean trolley based on Autodesk inventor professional; forecast on upsetting crack based on numerical simulation; theoretic and experimental research of crankshafts barrel finishing; influence of wire grid on the cone calorimeter results of textile fabrics; 3D numerical analysis about effect of seal clearance on labyrinth seal performance; the nonlinear phenomenon in modal analysis of liquid tank; modeling of direct current atmospheric pressure argon discharge in two-dimensional; numerical analysis on temperature field of electric connectors; performance analysis of chaotic spread spectrum sequences; computer simulation of pore-water pressure; TQLZ self-balance vibrating screen static and modal analysis; coupled thermal analysis on carbide anvil of cubic press; a new approach to assemble tolerance analysis based on CE/TOL; pro/ENGINEER and 3DS max combined with virtools for virtual reality application; chromatic adaptation and chromatic adaptation transform issues in color appearance model; research on inductive power charging device of unmanned ground vehicle; design and simulation on hydraulic sleepless speed regulation system of invariable fertilizing application; distributed photovoltaic power generation system design and grid research; wide-area time-delay coordinating control of generator excitations and SVCs based on Hamiltonian functional method; the lagrangian of analytical mechanics and its application in power system with TCSC; ARM-based speed regulating system for asynchronous motor; research on improved small-disturbance model of doubly-fed wind generator; the design study on a novel MW wind power generation speed-up machine; optimization of smoothing control in hybrid wind and battery energy storage system; an improved Newton's method and its application in power system; multi-objective programming and time optimal algorithm research; optimal planning of distributed generation using self-organizing optimization algorithm; the application base on frame optimization method in the rectangular hole group position error; the analysis of circuit breaker health index and the characteristic quantity; bath central heating and air conditioning systems economic analysis; optimization of exit design based on evacuation model for limited visibility; ecological-economic values of lignocellulosic herbaceous plant on contaminated land; the key-factor modulation of waste tire pyrolysis in resource chemical plant for recovered fuel production; the applicant feasibility study of recovered fuel after waste tire pyrolysis; pollutants concentrations in ambient air and their relationship in the spring of Beijing; research on preparation and properties of biodiesel; two-phase mesophilic anaerobic co-digestion of food waste and sewage sludge; accelerated biodegradation of PLA nonwovens in soil bacterial suspensions.
