TI  - A Quantum Chemistry Insight into the Potential Role of the Singlet Oxygen-Acetone System as a Source for Production of Stable Secondary Organic Aerosols through a Multiwell Multipath Reaction
PY  - 2025
T2  - Journal of Physical Chemistry A
VL  - 129
IS  - 1
SP  - 207
EP  - 221
